name: makhoof
description:
Weapons with high destructive power
Can be used in land and air wars
Has more than 10 suicide drones with high destructive power
Has the ability to manage and command more than 10 drones simultaneously.
It has two high-precision nuclear ballistic missiles with a range of more than 500 km.
There is no need to supply energy due to the use of cosmic energy
This means that it can continue to patrol for a very long time
